{"title":"试飞员之歌","authors":["赵家栋"],"dates":[{"year":1997,"month":8,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"试飞员之歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵家栋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"试飞员"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重新填满一页飞行记录"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又与一个丰收季节匆匆告别"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随之"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那被激越情怀烧红的云朵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也飘然飞回昨天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金黄灿灿的阳光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把机身抚摸得如此晶莹剔透"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一腔豪情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那对蓝天的一脉诚意"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在蓦然变得异常寂静的机坪上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉睡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连同那悠悠思绪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也靠到天地博大的胸怀里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"编织着精美奇妙的梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"充满伤感的爱情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也终于振奋起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿透凝重的寒夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和柔情的春意"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去拥抱八月的火辣太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拥抱天空和大地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在那寒冷的季节里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我受伤的诗歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾从云端跌落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然而"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那呻吟的旋律中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仍饱含期冀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和不息地奋争"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高科技伴随如铁意志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电脑携带着浪漫热情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于把我的诗歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修补得非常非常完美"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流线型体魄光滑似镜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"螺旋桨线条异常精妙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与伤痛和昨天道别吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驾驭钢翅向天宇翱翔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那鲜艳的八一军旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正在遥远的北方猎猎飘荡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把辽阔无际的天幕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渲染得热烈辉煌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辉煌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者单位：中国航空工业总公司保定五五○厂）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}